## 7. Converter Agents — The 2-Tier Strategy

[converter_agents/base.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/base.py)

Every converter agent follows the same `BaseConverterAgent` inner loop:

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["Read Java Source"] --> B["Read Contract (.md)"]
    B --> C["Parse to IR (javalang/regex)"]
    C --> D{"Tier 1: Deterministic?"}
    D -->|"Yes"| E["Generate code via templates"]
    D -->|"No"| F{"LLM Available?"}
    F -->|"No"| G["Generate TODO scaffold"]
    F -->|"Yes"| H["Tier 2: LLM Synthesis"]
    
    E --> I["Syntax Check"]
    G --> I
    H --> I
    
    I -->|"Fail"| J["LLM Self-Correct"]
    J --> I
    I -->|"Pass"| K["Check Imports"]
    K --> L{"Stub Methods?"}
    L -->|"Yes"| J
    L -->|"No"| M["Resolve Imports + Write Output"]
```

### Tier 1: Deterministic Conversion

[converter_tools.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/tools/converter_tools.py)

Used for simple, pattern-matchable components:
- `@Entity` with only basic fields → SQLAlchemy model with `Mapped` columns, ForeignKey relationships
- Repository interface with ≤2 methods → Basic CRUD repository class

Includes:
- **Java type → SQLAlchemy column mapping** (String→String(255), Long→Integer, LocalDateTime→DateTime, etc.)
- **JPA relationship handling** (ManyToOne→ForeignKey+relationship, OneToMany→relationship, ManyToMany→secondary table)
- **JPQL → SQLAlchemy translation** via the [JPQLTranslator](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/tools/jpql_translator.py)

### Tier 2: LLM Synthesis

When deterministic conversion isn't possible (complex services, controllers with business logic):

1. Loads the specialized prompt template from [prompts/](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/prompts)
2. Injects context: Java source, contract, existing generated code, docs, technologies
3. Calls the LLM with strict system instructions (no markdown fences, only valid Python, `app.` package root)
4. Strips fences, sanitizes placeholder imports

### Inner Validation Loop (up to 3 retries for services)

After LLM generates code:
1. **Syntax check** via `ast.parse()` — if fails, asks LLM to fix
2. **Import resolution** — rewrites imports using the `output_registry` mapping
3. **Stub detection** — for services/controllers/repos, AST-walks to find methods with empty bodies (`pass`, `return None`, `raise NotImplementedError`) and forces LLM retry with explicit error message

### Converter Agent Registry

| Agent | Source | Target | Key Features |
|-------|--------|--------|-------------|
| [model_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/model_converter.py) | `@Entity` | SQLAlchemy model | Deterministic for simple entities |
| [schema_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/schema_converter.py) | DTO classes | Pydantic schemas | Bean Validation → Field validators |
| [repo_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/repo_converter.py) | `JpaRepository` | SQLAlchemy repo | JPQL translation, query method names |
| [service_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/service_converter.py) | `@Service` | Python service class | 3 inner retries, cross-layer context |
| [controller_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/controller_converter.py) | `@RestController` | FastAPI router | Request mapping translation |
| [exception_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/exception_converter.py) | `@ControllerAdvice` | Exception handlers | Maps to FastAPI exception_handler |
| [feign_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/feign_converter.py) | `@FeignClient` | httpx async client | External service calls |
| [event_consumer_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/event_consumer_converter.py) | `@KafkaListener` / `@RabbitListener` | Async consumers | aiokafka / aio-pika |
| [scheduler_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/converter_agents/scheduler_converter.py) | `@Scheduled` | APScheduler jobs | Cron/interval translation |
| [config_converter](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/migration_subgraph/converter_nodes.py#L158-L436) | — | Infrastructure files | **Deterministic, no LLM** |

### Config Converter (Special Case)

The config converter is the only one that runs **without an LLM**. It generates all infrastructure files deterministically:

- `app/main.py` — FastAPI entry point with CORS, lifespan, scheduler
- `app/core/config.py` — Pydantic Settings (adapts to discovered tech: Redis URL, Kafka bootstrap, Feign client URLs)
- `app/db/session.py` + `app/db/base.py` — Async SQLAlchemy engine/session
- `app/api/v1/router.py` — Auto-imports all discovered controllers
- `requirements.txt` — Dynamically includes packages based on discovered technologies
- `app/core/security.py` — JWT auth stubs (only if Spring Security detected)
- All `__init__.py` package files

