## 10. Final Assembly & Output

[assemble.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/nodes/assemble.py)

The assemble node post-processes the generated project:

1. **Sanitize imports** — Replaces placeholder package names (`yourapp`, `myapp`) with `app`
2. **Backfill infrastructure** — Generates any missing core files (db/base.py, db/session.py, deps.py, security.py)
3. **Docker scaffolding** — [docker_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/generators/docker_generator.py): Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml
4. **Alembic scaffolding** — [alembic_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/generators/alembic_generator.py): Migration config + initial migration
5. **Test scaffolding** — [test_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/agents/generators/test_generator.py): pytest fixtures + test stubs for each component
6. **ZIP packaging** — Archives the entire output directory as `fastapi_project_{job_id}.zip`

