## 12. Frontend & Persistence

### Supabase (Job Tracking)
- [supabase_client.py](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast/app/supabase_client.py) provides a `get_supabase()` singleton
- The `migration_jobs` table stores: id, source_type, source_url, branch, status, current_step, progress_pct, error_message, output_path, created_at, completed_at
- Progress is updated both from the orchestrator (per-node) and from converter nodes (per-component via `_push_progress()`)

### Filesystem (State & Artifacts)
- `workspace/{job_id}/artifacts/_state.json` — Full serialized `MigrationState` for frontend polling
- Analysis artifacts are numbered markdown files: `01-technology-inventory.md`, `02-business-rules.md`, `03-component-inventory.md`, etc.
- `workspace/{job_id}/contracts/` — Per-component business logic contracts

### Frontend
- Vite + React app in [spring2fast-ui/](file:///c:/Users/Musharraf/Documents/Gen-AI/spring2fast-ui)
- Polls `/state` endpoint for real-time progress visualization
- Displays source/output file trees, artifacts with markdown rendering

